DESCRIPTION:Dance\, laugh\, and let loose\, an early-bird party just for the ladies! Great music\, good vibes\, and home by 10.\nGrab your girlfriends and hit the dance floor for a fun\, feel-good night out\, without the late-night hangover! This ladies-only early-bird dance party is all about great music\, high energy\, and celebrating friendship in style.\nCome ready to move\, mingle\, and make memories before the clock strikes bedtime. It’s the perfect mix of fun and freedom\, no pressure\, no drama\, just good vibes and great company.\nFeaturing DJ Dyops!\nDoors open at 5:30pm\nMusic plays 6:00pm-9:00pm\nTickets $19 advance $26 at door. AGES 18+ LADIES ONLY
