SUMMARY:The Dictator Tots at the Penngrove Pub
DESCRIPTION:The Dictator Tots are a band dedicated to playing Jammy Prog Shite. Based in Petaluma\, the band focuses on original material and creative on the spot improvisation. \nThe Dictator Tots are a Sonoma County-based band\, often performing at venues like The Big Easy in Petaluma. Known for a fun\, energetic live sound\, the band features Pete Hale (vocals/guitar)\, Bob McBain (keys)\, Brad Hoffman (drums)\, and Steve Hoffman (bass). They are a local music staple in the Petaluma area. \n 
