SUMMARY:Last Mic Standing: Comedy Showdown
DESCRIPTION:MERCY PRESENTS: \nLast Mic Standing: Comedy Showdown \nBattle for the Main Stage. \nOn Friday\, April 3rd from 8PM – 9:30PM\, eight fearless comics step into the spotlight for one night of rapid-fire punchlines\, crowd reactions\, and high-stakes humor inside The Lounge at Mercy. \nThis isn’t an open mic. \nThis is a showdown. \n8 Comics. 3 Judges. Audience Vote. \nEach comedian brings their sharpest material and strongest stage presence to compete for the title of Last Mic Standing. Judges score the sets. The crowd weighs in. The energy decides everything. \nOne night. One winner. \nThe stakes are real. The winner takes home a $100 cash prize and earns a paid hosting spot at the next Mercy’s Tokes and Jokes Comedy Night. Win the crowd. Own the mic. Come back as host. \nComics sign up here and get a free entry to the event: https://bit.ly/lastmicsignup Names will be drawn from a hat day of the event. \nThis is a 420-friendly comedy competition hosted inside our fully licensed cannabis consumption lounge\, where elevated vibes meet elevated punchlines. Guests are welcome to enjoy responsibly while comics go head-to-head under the lights. Great sets hit different here. \nTicket Tiers:\n$20 – General Admission (Open Seating) Entry to Comedy Showdown Open seating (first come\, first served). Come early for the best spot.\n$30 – GA + Goodie Bag A little extra Entry + goodie bag ($15 value) included. Open seating (first come\, first served).\n* $40 – Preferred Bucket Seat + Goodie Bag (Most Popular) Comfort upgrade * Guaranteed bucket seat + shared table access\, plus goodie bag ($15 value) included. Limited seating.\n$135 – Couch Crew Pass (3 Guests + Premium Bag) Bring your crew Includes admission for 3 guests\, reserved couch seating with a dedicated table\, plus premium bag ($100 value) included. Only 11 couches. \n21+ Only | DCC # C12-0000420-LIC \nURLs:\nTickets: https://go.evvnt.com/3543113-0?pid=5514\nInstagram: https://go.evvnt.com/3543113-2?pid=5514 \nPrices:\nGeneral Admission: USD 20.00\,\nGeneral Admission + $15 Goodie Bag: USD 30.00\,\nPreferred Bucket Seat + $15 Goodie Bag: USD 40.00\,\nCouch Crew Pass (3 Guests + $100 Goodie Bag: USD 135.00 \nCategory: Classes / Courses | Creative and Performing Arts | Comedy \nDate and Time: Friday April 03\, 2026 at 8:00 pm to 9:30 pm \nVenue details: The Lounge at Mercy\, 7950 Redwood Drive\, Cotati\, California\, 94931\, United States
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/last-mic-standing-comedy-showdown-2/
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy\, 7950 Redwood Drive\, Cotati\, 94931
CATEGORIES:Comedy
GEO:38.33308;-122.71387
