SUMMARY:Pop-Off!- Dance Party
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma County’s newest queer dance party—an all-out celebration of pop music\, community\, and unapologetic joy.\nSonoma County Queer Community- get ready to pop off! Pop Off is brand-new\, pop-up\, all pop queer dance party!\nPop-Off! is Sonoma County’s newest queer dance party—an all-out celebration of pop music\, community\, and unapologetic joy. Making its debut Friday\, April 3rd at The California Theatre in downtown Santa Rosa\, this brand-new pop-up party invites you to hit the dance floor and lose yourself in the songs you know by heart.\nAll night long\, DJ Mario will keep the energy high\, spinning nothing but pop—from iconic throwbacks to the biggest hits of today. Whether you’re screaming along to your favorite diva anthem or discovering your new dance-floor obsession\, Pop-Off! is the place where Sonoma County’s queer community comes together to celebrate\, dance\, and let the pop music take over.\nCOCKTAILS | POP MUSIC | DANCE PARTY | GO-GO DANCERS\nPRESALE $15 | $20 AT THE DOOR\nProduced by THTR Productions — the team behind Drag Brunch at The Flamingo Resort\, the summer entertainment at the r3 Hotel\, Sonoma County Pride after parties\, and former co-producers of the iconic Lush Queer Party at The Flamingo Resort — you already know this party is going to be lit!\nThis party is for the queer community\, however allies are welcomed guests. Any homophobia\, transphobia\, racism\, xenophobia\, or hate of any kind will not be tolerated.\nPRESALE $15 | $20 AT THE DOOR\nAdditional tix available at\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/pop-off-queer-dance-party-tickets-1985110717594 \nDoors open at 9:30pm Tickets $15 online. $20 at door.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/pop-off-dance-party/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Other,Recreation
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Pop-off.jpg
GEO:38.44252;-122.71621
