SUMMARY:Celebrate Easter with the Russian River Railbikes
DESCRIPTION:Russian River Railbikes – Easter Weekend Experience Elevate your Easter weekend with an enjoyable railbike journey through the heart of Sonoma County. Glide along historic railway lines to the Russian River\, surrounded by rolling vineyards\, blooming wildflowers\, and serene spring landscapes to the turn around point overlooking the Russian River with picnic tables and Easter surprises for kids. \nWhen: Easter Weekend (Saturday & Sunday departures) \nDuration: Approximately 1.5–2 hours\, including a riverside pause \nRailbikes: Accommodates 2–4 guests per bike \nCost: From ~$45 per guest or ~$145 per railbike \nAn ideal escape for couples\, families\, or small groups seeking a distinctive and elevated outdoor experience. Availability is limited for the holiday weekend—early reservations are strongly encouraged.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/celebrate-easter-with-the-russian-river-railbikes-2/
LOCATION:Russian River Railbikes\, 425 Asti Road\, Cloverdale\, 95425
CATEGORIES:Kids and Family,Recreation
END:VEVENT
