SUMMARY:Easter Egg Hunt & Wine Tasting
DESCRIPTION:Saturday\, April 4\, 2026\n10 a.m. to 12 p.m. | Family-friendly\n$35 per person 21 & older | Reservations required \nCelebrate Easter weekend at Dry Creek Vineyard with a springtime experience designed for the whole family. Begin with a relaxed Easter egg hunt on the lawn\, where young guests can discover eggs filled with small treasures. Then\, shift gears with a seated tasting of a thoughtfully selected flight of our limited-production wines for the grown-ups — the perfect way to toast the season. \nLimited to 12 parties. Maximum of 6 guests per party.
