SUMMARY:OAEC Nursery Grand Reopening
DESCRIPTION:We’re excited to announce that the OAEC Nursery is reopening on April 3rd!\nTo celebrate\, the nursery will be open from 11 AM to 5 PM on both April 3rd and 4th with live music! We are also hosting a public garden tour at 1:00 PM on Saturday\, April 4th.\nAfter taking the 2025 season off\, we are getting ready to open the doors again to our plant-loving community for our nonprofit fundraising plant sale. The nursery will continue to be a wild celebration of biodiversity – uplifting ecologically and culturally important plants\, focusing on perennial food\, medicinal\, and native varieties\, and continuing to offer a well-curated and ever-evolving selection of annual food crops.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/oaec-nursery-grand-reopening/2026-04-04/
LOCATION:Occidental Arts and Ecology Center\, 15290 Coleman Valley Rd\, Occidental\, CA\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids and Family,Music,Other
END:VEVENT
