SUMMARY:Swap-A-Luma! Petaluma’s Premier Clothing Swap and FUNdraiser
DESCRIPTION:It’s SPRING 🌸 and that means it’s time for another Swap-A-Luma! FUNdraiser and Community Clothing swap! \nRefresh your style\, help the environment and give back while you swap. Come for the clothing\, stay for the joyful community! \nEnjoy a high vibe\, organized\, and enjoyable boutique style swapping experience in an inclusive\, artful and lively environment. \nFashion show at 2pm\, yummy taco truck and a special mystery guest! 😃 \nBy participating\, you help keep textiles out of overflowing landfills\, reducing environmental impact and supporting a more sustainable future. \nIt’s a party with a\npurpose! ✨ \n🩵💙🩵 Proceeds will benefit Cool Petaluma www.coolpetaluma.org \, a wonderful organization that brings Petalumans together to learn\, collaborate\, and take collective steps toward a healthier\, planet-friendly community. Join us!
