SUMMARY:Hop Stoopid Beer Release w/Solid Air Band at Lagunitas
DESCRIPTION:Solid Air is a music group based north of San Francisco\, led by co-founders Allegra Broughton (vocals\, guitar)\, and Sam Page (vocals\, bass\, baritone slide guitar)\, native Californians who have been performing for over thirty years at fairs\, festivals\, clubs\, concert stages\, wineries\, coffeehouses and private events. Solid Air performs as a duo\, trio and full band with high energy vocals\, stellar musicianship\, top-notch original songs and eclectic covers from jug band to cajun to classic rock ‘n’ roll for both listening and dancing\, with references available.
